\v 23 As <a name="02403602300010" ll="SDBH:יְהוּדִי:000002:Names of People">Jehudi</a> <a name="02403602300008" ll="SDBH:קרא:000001:Shout">read</a> <a name="02403602300012" ll="SDBH:שָׁלֹשׁ:000000:Quantity|Frequency">three</a> or <a name="02403602300018" ll="SDBH:אַרְבַּע:000000:Quantity|Frequency">four</a> <a name="02403602300014" ll="SDBH:דֶּלֶת:000005:Parts: Scrolls">columns</a>, the king would <a name="02403602300020" ll="SDBH:קרע:000000:Detach">cut</a> them <a name="02403602300020" ll="SDBH:קרע:000000:Detach">off</a> with a <a name="02403602300028" ll="SDBH:סֹופֵר:000000:Officials" il="NBGpb20140728b">penknife</a> and <a name="02403602300032" ll="SDBH:שׁלך:000000:Move">throw</a> them into the <a name="02403602300038" ll="SDBH:אֵשׁ:000000:Fire" il="Fire02">fire</a> in the <a name="02403602300046" ll="SDBH:אָח:001000:Furnaces">brazier</a>, until the <a name="02403602300052">entire</a> <a name="02403602300056" ll="SDBH:מְגִלָּה:000000:Scrolls" il="HK00282;Realia:1.7.1a;NBGpb20140728b;Torah">scroll</a> was <a name="02403602300050" ll="SDBH:תמם:000000:Non-Exist">consumed</a> in the <a name="02403602300062" ll="SDBH:אֵשׁ:000000:Fire" il="Fire02">fire</a> that was in the <a name="02403602300070" ll="SDBH:אָח:001000:Furnaces">brazier</a>.
\v 24 Yet neither the <a name="02403602400020" ll="SDBH:מֶלֶךְ:000000:Leaders">king</a>, nor <a name="02403602400024">any</a> of his <a name="02403602400026" ll="SDBH:עֶבֶד:000000:Classes|Officials|Serve" il="Bolen00049">servants</a> who <a name="02403602400030">heard</a> <a name="02403602400034">all</a> these <a name="02403602400038" ll="SDBH:דָּבָר:000003:Happen|Speak">words</a>, <a name="02403602400006" ll="SDBH:פחד:000000:Shake">was</a> <a name="02403602400006" ll="SDBH:פחד:000000:Shake">afraid</a>, nor did they <a name="02403602400012" ll="SDBH:קרע:000000:Detach">rend</a> their <a name="02403602400016" ll="SDBH:בֶּגֶד:000001:Clothing" il="NBGmk20140519a;NBGmk20140519c;NBGmk20140519d">garments</a>.
